= Custom Houdini Procedural = 
#context: lop
#icon: opdef:.?gear-svgrepo-com.svg

"""Customize Houdini Procedural Primitve"""

== Overview ==
Make specified primitive to present Houdini procedural

WARNING:
     Render command must has argument *--allowed-procedurals all* if not only curves and points

@parameters
Graph File:
    #id: graph_file
    Graph file provided from sop level
    
Procedural Name:
    #id: proc_name
    The name of Houdini Procedural
    
Procedural Primtive:
    #id: proc_prim
    The primitive will be Houdini procedural
    
Inputs:
    #id: inputs
    Specify primitive to be input of graph
    
Overrides:
    #id: overrides
    Specify parm of graph and properity of USD primitive